# John Stick

**Env:** Local secrets in **`.env.local`** (from **`.env.example`**). Never prefix API keys with **`VITE_`** (Vite inlines them into the browser bundle).

**Tooling (details: `docs/TOOLCHAIN_ACCESS.md`):**

- **Blender** — agents can drive it via **MCP** when the Blender add-on is connected (see `.cursor/mcp.json`).
- **`ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`** — **audio asset** generation (TTS / SFX / related) in **local scripts only**, not shipped to the client.
- **`GEMINI_API_KEY`** — **image asset** generation and image understanding in **local scripts only**.

**How we work:** Pragmatic, **brief**, **YAGNI**. **Code is liability** — less code, no duplication, stay organized, keep the repo clean. Same for **docs and assets**: one canonical place for each fact; delete or merge instead of piling alternates.

**Layout contract:** `docs/REPO_CONVENTIONS.md`. **Vision / backlog:** `docs/GAME_PLAN.md`, `docs/TODO.md`.
